:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 25, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104yvg1665702759219.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/yvg1665702759219.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/yvg1665702759219.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"yvg1665702759219\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Starts a new element using the name, including optional prefix and URI\n      elements.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"yvg1665702759219__topic_d136526e1_d136527e1_d136528e1\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104yvg1665702759219_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"yvg1665702759219__codeblock_v1y_j1h_hwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">STARTELEMENT (Prefix,ElementName,URI)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yvg1665702759219__section_gh4_l1h_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1119196e56\">Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"yvg1665702759219__table_d16292e1_d16293e1_d16294e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">STARTELEMENT parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"yvg1665702759219__table_d16292e1_d16293e1_d16294e1__entry__1\">Parameter</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"yvg1665702759219__table_d16292e1_d16293e1_d16294e1__entry__2\">Data Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"yvg1665702759219__table_d16292e1_d16293e1_d16294e1__entry__3\">Direction</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"yvg1665702759219__table_d16292e1_d16293e1_d16294e1__entry__4\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yvg1665702759219__table_d16292e1_d16293e1_d16294e1__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Prefix</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yvg1665702759219__table_d16292e1_d16293e1_d16294e1__entry__2\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yvg1665702759219__table_d16292e1_d16293e1_d16294e1__entry__3\"> IN</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yvg1665702759219__table_d16292e1_d16293e1_d16294e1__entry__4\"> Namespace ID prefixed to the\n                           <var class=\"keyword varname\">ElementName</var> and <var class=\"keyword varname\">URI</var> elements, if\n                        they are specified; maximum length is 40 bytes.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yvg1665702759219__table_d16292e1_d16293e1_d16294e1__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">ElementName</var></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yvg1665702759219__table_d16292e1_d16293e1_d16294e1__entry__2\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yvg1665702759219__table_d16292e1_d16293e1_d16294e1__entry__3\">IN</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yvg1665702759219__table_d16292e1_d16293e1_d16294e1__entry__4\">Element name; mandatory; maximum length is 255\n                        bytes.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yvg1665702759219__table_d16292e1_d16293e1_d16294e1__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">URI</var></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yvg1665702759219__table_d16292e1_d16293e1_d16294e1__entry__2\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yvg1665702759219__table_d16292e1_d16293e1_d16294e1__entry__3\">IN</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yvg1665702759219__table_d16292e1_d16293e1_d16294e1__entry__4\">URL or other URI for the namespace; maximum\n                        length is 512 bytes.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yvg1665702759219__section_vs4_t1h_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1119196e156\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"yvg1665702759219__p_d136721e1_d136722e1_d136723e1\">Values returned:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"yvg1665702759219__ul_r1b_v1h_hwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"yvg1665702759219__li_d48317e1_d48318e1_d48319e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code> Success. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"yvg1665702759219__li_d48320e1_d48321e1_d48322e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">–1</code> Failure. Called in an illegal sequence. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yvg1665702759219__section_d1l_v1h_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1119196e180\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"yvg1665702759219__p_d136544e1_d136545e1_d136546e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">STARTELEMENT</span> operation\n            inserts the beginning of an element tag. The closing bracket of the open element tag\n               (<code class=\"ph codeph\">&gt;</code>) is added by subsequent operation calls. The UXMLWRITER\n            component ensures that the result is legal XML, so you need not concern yourself with\n            this. It is indented with spaces if it is a nested element.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"yvg1665702759219__p_d136547e1_d136548e1_d136549e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">STARTELEMENT</span> can specify a\n            namespace using the Prefix and URI. To specy additional namespaces, use the\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">ADDPREFIXMAPPING</span> operation.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"yvg1665702759219__p_d136550e1_d136551e1_d136552e1\">This operation must follow a call to\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">STARTDOCUMENT</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">ENDELEMENT</span> (to close a previous\n            element), <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">STARTELEMENT</span> (to create an element nested inside another),\n            or <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">DOCCOMMENT</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"yvg1665702759219__p_d136553e1_d136554e1_d136555e1\">Assuming that <code class=\"ph codeph\">uxm1</code> is an instance\n            of UXMLWRITER, the following examples insert the indicated text into the XML document\n            managed by <code class=\"ph codeph\">uxml1</code>, indented with spaces if it is a nested element:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"yvg1665702759219__ul_tt2_x1h_hwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"yvg1665702759219__li_d48287e1_d48288e1_d48289e1\">Add <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;Aaa2</code>:\n               <div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104yvg1665702759219_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"yvg1665702759219__codeblock_wv5_x1h_hwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">uxml1-&gt;startElement(\"\", \"Aaa2\", \"\")</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"yvg1665702759219__li_d48290e1_d48291e1_d48292e1\">Add <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;hoi:Aaa1</code>:\n               <div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104yvg1665702759219_html_2\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"yvg1665702759219__codeblock_p5b_z1h_hwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">uxml1-&gt;startElement(\"hoi\", \"Aaa1\", \"a/b/c\")</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"yvg1665702759219__li_d48293e1_d48294e1_d48295e1\">Add <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;hoi:Aaa1</code>:\n               <div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104yvg1665702759219_html_3\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"yvg1665702759219__codeblock_l3h_1bh_hwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">uxml1-&gt;startElement(\"hoi\", \"Aaa1\", \"\")</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"yvg1665702759219__li_d48296e1_d48297e1_d48298e1\">Add <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;Aaa1 xmlns=\"a/b/c\"</code>:\n               <div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104yvg1665702759219_html_4\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"yvg1665702759219__codeblock_fbl_bbh_hwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">uxml1-&gt;startElement(\"\", \"Aaa1\", \"a/b/c\")</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rqe1665703206044.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>ADDPREFIXMAPPING</a><p>Adds a namespace to the beginning of an element tag.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534287\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534287\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "STARTELEMENT Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 25, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Starts a new element using the name, including optional prefix and URI elements. Explain this code STARTELEMENT (Prefix,ElementName,URI) Copy Parameters Table 1. STARTELEMENT parameters Parameter Data Type Direction Description Prefix String IN Namespace ID prefixed to the ElementName and URI elements, if they are specified; maximum length is 40 bytes. ElementName String IN Element name; mandatory; maximum length is 255 bytes. URI String IN URL or other URI for the namespace; maximum length is 512 bytes. Return Values Values returned: 0 Success. –1 Failure. Called in an illegal sequence. Description The STARTELEMENT operation inserts the beginning of an element tag. The closing bracket of the open element tag ( > ) is added by subsequent operation calls. The UXMLWRITER component ensures that the result is legal XML, so you need not concern yourself with this. It is indented with spaces if it is a nested element. The STARTELEMENT can specify a namespace using the Prefix and URI. To specy additional namespaces, use the ADDPREFIXMAPPING operation. This operation must follow a call to STARTDOCUMENT , ENDELEMENT (to close a previous element), STARTELEMENT (to create an element nested inside another), or DOCCOMMENT . Assuming that uxm1 is an instance of UXMLWRITER, the following examples insert the indicated text into the XML document managed by uxml1 , indented with spaces if it is a nested element: Add <Aaa2 : Explain this code uxml1->startElement(\"\", \"Aaa2\", \"\") Copy Add <hoi:Aaa1 : Explain this code uxml1->startElement(\"hoi\", \"Aaa1\", \"a/b/c\") Copy Add <hoi:Aaa1 : Explain this code uxml1->startElement(\"hoi\", \"Aaa1\", \"\") Copy Add <Aaa1 xmlns=\"a/b/c\" : Explain this code uxml1->startElement(\"\", \"Aaa1\", \"a/b/c\") Copy Related Links ADDPREFIXMAPPING Adds a namespace to the beginning of an element tag. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}